data.description: Welcome to this charming 1502 square foot home nestled deep in the heart of Hico, TX. This delightful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house boasts a rustic aesthetic with its rock and wood construction. The third bedroom offers incredible versatility, serving as either a comfortable bedroom or a spacious game or media room. The well-appointed and roomy kitchen provides ample space for culinary endeavors and entertaining guests. Situated on nearly half an acre, this property offers a generous backyard, partially fenced for added privacy. The back area offers flexibility, providing room for storing extra vehicles or trailers, as well as the potential for creating inviting outdoor grilling or sitting areas. Located in close proximity to an array of delightful restaurants and retail stores, including Green Canoe Outfitters, Blue Star Trading Company, and Wiseman House Chocolates, this property immerses you in the vibrant heart of Hico's cultural and culinary scene.
